  "name": "Ectoplasm Bloodline",
  "permission": {
    "default": 0
  },
  "type": "feat",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Your family has a connection with the ethereal substance known as ectoplasm, whether from communing with the spirits or battling the spiritual&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Undead\">undead</a>. The power of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/environment/the-planes#TOC-Ethereal-Plane\">Ethereal Plane</a>&nbsp;thrums in your mind and pulls at your flesh.</em></p>\n<div>\n<p><strong>Class Skill</strong>:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/stealth\">Stealth</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Bonus Spells:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.tuh5vc2bojaws3ig]{Obscuring Mist}&nbsp;(3rd),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.vmamex3k9tpm5jex]{Ghost Whip}&nbsp;(5th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.clo5w5mow21nln10]{Ectoplasmic Snare}&nbsp;(7th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.c99w6rm28rpz14xu]{Spirit-Bound Blade} (9th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.wc5oz0ozbazl1k6o]{Wall Of Ectoplasm}&nbsp;(11th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.btccs4sjo2nog1a0]{Ethereal Jaunt} (13th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.8fyg16j34uruuy45]{Ectoplasmic Eruption}&nbsp;(15th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.wniqskqkk0cubu9u]{Create Demiplane}&nbsp;(17th),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.gw9bes9othfqm7mi]{Etherealness}&nbsp;(19th).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bonus Feats</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.pmAO1Sni8xx71pLF]{Blind-Fight},</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.JreaiTHdyWFNj3Tb]{Dodge},&nbsp;</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/metamagic-feats/ectoplasmic-spell-metamagic\">Ectoplasmic Spell</a>,</li>\n<li>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/metamagic-feats/lingering-spell-metamagic\">Lingering Spell</a>,</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.2YuxcUNFMPNBpekG]{Silent Spell},</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.7zJTztNW7hdaqjKc]{Skill Focus}&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/fly\">Fly</a>),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.7zJTztNW7hdaqjKc]{Skill Focus}&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/stealth\">Stealth</a>),</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.feats.V2zY7BltkpSXwejy]{Spell Focus}.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Arcana:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/universal-monster-rules#TOC-Incorporeal-Ex-\">Incorporeal</a>&nbsp;creatures take 75% of the normal amount of damage from your damaging spells, and when&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Incorporeal\">incorporeal</a>&nbsp;creatures attempt saving throws against your non-damaging spells, they roll twice and must take the lower result.</p>\n</div>",
